d under this Act must be dealt with in a Magistrates&rsquo; Court. The maximum sentence that the Court can impose for an offence under the Football (Offences) Act 1991 is a fine of up to &pound;1000. Of course when imposing any sort of financial penalty the Court must have regard to a person&rsquo;s financial circumstances. Each of the offences set out above are offences for which the court must make a Football Banning Order if satisfied that there are reasonable grounds to believe that it would help to prevent violence or disorder at football matches."},{"pid":"ce7f72a9e3f52f097e1614039863a125a0bbb401","tid":1499864,"uid":116722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"自推，無恥地希望大家同我一齊brainstorm 我份coursework"},{"pid":"5eec32ee2bedfe9b60fd26793c4eab1c81a7f345","tid":1499864,"uid":230537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8aa8248d3ba40142f6e070c5c3d0390e2ad2834","tid":1499864,"uid":116722,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d16e37b57d93b7bff295f90d6db30ef15ea121bc","tid":1499864,"uid":56537,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"巴打我有諗過 不過你要係靚女大波先有呢效果"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"如果同時有兩個人呢? 一個扮曱甴，一個用假武器追住佢作勢打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"好似幾好，"},{"pid":"be47af83a6875caed3485da33b00eb45a8c0eff4","tid":1499864,"uid":116722,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5eec32ee2bedfe9b60fd26793c4eab1c81a7f345","tid":1499864,"uid":230537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8aa8248d3ba40142f6e070c5c3d0390e2ad2834","tid":1499864,"uid":116722,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d16e37b57d93b7bff295f90d6db30ef15ea121bc","tid":1499864,"uid":56537,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"巴打我有諗過 不過你要係靚女大波先有呢效果"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"如果同時有兩個人呢? 一個扮曱甴，一個用假武器追住佢作勢打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":